OL,5, Ex-Post Office investigator Stephen    
OL,6, Bradshaw has denied he and colleagues  
OL,7, behaved like "mafia gangsters" towards 
OL,8, wrongly accused sub-postmasters.       
OL,10,FMr Bradshaw was involved in the        
OL,11,Fcriminal investigation of nine         
OL,12,Fsub-postmasters and was giving evidence
OL,13,Fto the Post Office inquiry.            
OL,15,FHe denied intimidating or misleading   
OL,16,Fthe sub-postmasters he investigated.   
OL,18,FHundreds were wrongly prosecuted       
OL,19,Fbetween 1999 and 2015 after being      
OL,20,Ffalsely accused of stealing money.     
